3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a novel approach for text recognition using GANs and adversarial learning, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence.
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with text recognition, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the domain of computation and language.
